source.name: Fictitious B - Map Test
source.description:
Fictitious Business Names recorded with County of Alameda Auditor Recorder Office between Jan 1, 2008 to Dec 31, 2011.       
Type filing abbreviation descriptions: BST = Business Trust; COP = Co-Partners; COR = Corporation; GEN = General Partnership; HUS = Husband & Wife; IND = Individual; JVT = Joint Venture; LIA = Limited Liability Company; LIM = Limited Partnership; LLP = Limited Liability Partnership; OTH = Other; SDP = State or Local Registered; TST = A Trust; UNI = Unincorporated Association
